Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:09.29,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}湧上心頭的 感動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:19.38,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴著湛藍的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:23.74,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎風前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:30.42,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我陶醉時 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:35.28,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我們齊聲歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:42.55,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:49.33,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}無論何時 都想揮動雙手的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:53.62,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}確實是 曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:59.15,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}與你同在的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:03.50,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}永遠如 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:13.29,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}我們的前方 道路在延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:22.02,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}攀上 下一個陡坡後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:26.78,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}我們再相見吧
